- üìÑ **Pagination** - Built-in offset and cursor-based (Relay) pagination
- üìä **Ordering** - Sort results by any field with automatic ordering
support
- üîê **Authentication & Permissions** - Django auth integration with
flexible permission system
- ‚ú® **CRUD Mutations** - Auto-generated create, update, and delete
